        <show3D>3</show3D>
        <tabIndex>604</tabIndex>
        <tabStop/>
        <backColor>-2147483633</backColor>
        <bubbleHelp>If checked the system will search for cargo that
is on the top height, either at the level indicated by the Top
Position Height attribute, or the top cargo at  
any height (i.e. items that have no cargo overstowing them).  </bubbleHelp>
